headline: Keysight Named a Leader in 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for AI-Augmented Software Testing Tools
summary: SANTA ROSA, Calif., November 11, 2025--Keysight Technologies, Inc. (NYSE: KEYS) announced that it has been recognized as a Leader in the 2025 Gartner® Magic Quadrant™ for AI-Augmented Software Testing Tools. The report evaluates technology providers based on their vision and execution in the rapidly evolving market for AI-driven testing solutions.
